{
  "logNo": "110183697434",
  "title": "한약의 당뇨병 예방효과 연구논문",
  "addDate": "2014. 1. 20.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "parentCategoryNo": "32",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110183697434",
  "html_size": 209265,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110183697434\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110183697434\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<div class=\"NLM_sec NLM_sec_level_1\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(33,33,33); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 17px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">한약 처방이 전당뇨환자의 2형 당뇨로의 이행을 억제할수 있는지, 12개월의 단기 연구를 통해 그 효과를 관찰한 것입니다. </font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"Gulim\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"Gulim\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140120_297/isuhani_1390178649477anOFa_JPEG/imagesCAEH2V5M.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"240\" height=\"171\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 240px; rheight: 171px\" id=\"20140120_297/isuhani_1390178649477anOFa_JPEG/imagesCAEH2V5M.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A775CC1A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140120_297/isuhani_1390178649477anOFa_JPEG/imagesCAEH2V5M.jpg?type=w3\"></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"Gulim\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">420명의 내당능 환자에게 각각 한약 혹은 위약을 투여한 후 3개월마다 당부하 검사 등을 통해 경과를 관찰한 결과, </font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"Gulim\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">한약처방군에서 당뇨가 발생한 확률은 18.18% 이고, </font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"Gulim\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">위약투여군에서는 29.32%로, </font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"Gulim\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><u><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><u><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\"><u>한약처방은 절대치로는 11.14%의 당뇨 발생을 억제하였으며, </u></span></u></span></u></span></u></strong></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"Gulim\"><strong><u></u></strong></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><u><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><u><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\"><u>상대치로는 당뇨의 발생을 절반 가까이 억제할수 있었음을 보인 것입니다.</u></span></u></span></u></span> </u></strong></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"Gulim\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">1년이라는 짧은 기간동안 이뤄진 연구라는 한계는 존재하지만, </font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">익히 잘 알려진바와 같이 한약처방은 다양한 만성질환의 예방과 치료에 효과적임이 </font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><font face=\"나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">계속 과학적으로 증명되어가고 있다는것을 이러한 연구가 보여주고 있네요.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\">&nbsp;</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"NLM_sec NLM_sec_level_1\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-55Roma, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(33,33,33); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 17px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>\r\n<div style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); LINE-HEIGHT: 20px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140120_104/isuhani_139017864918679Mld_JPEG/%B4%E7%B4%A2_diabet.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"275\" height=\"183\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 275px; rheight: 183px\" id=\"20140120_104/isuhani_139017864918679Mld_JPEG/%B4%E7%B4%A2_diabet.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A775CC1A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140120_104/isuhani_139017864918679Mld_JPEG/%B4%E7%B4%A2_diabet.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 20px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 20px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 20px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articleMeta\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-55Roma, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: auto auto 1em; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; WIDTH: 580px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">\r\n<div class=\"publicationContentTitle\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 30px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<h1 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 26px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-57Cn, 'Arial Narrow', helvetica, arial, sans-serif; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(68,102,125); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Chinese Herbal Medicine Tianqi Reduces Progression From Impaired Glucose Tolerance to Diabetes: A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Multicenter Trial</span></h1></div>\r\n<div class=\"articleMetaDrop publicationContentDropZone\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"publicationContentAuthors\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 19px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Lian%2C+F&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Fengmei Lian</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Li%2C+G&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Guangwei Li</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Chen%2C+X&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Xinyan Chen</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class