IZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Liu%2C+Y&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Yajun Liu</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Zhang%2C+R&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Rongfang Zhang</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Hao%2C+J&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Jianjun Hao</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Zhu%2C+Z&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Zhangzhi Zhu</span></a>,</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Li%2C+H&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Huilin Li</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Fang+Liu%2C+H&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Hong Fang Liu</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Cao%2C+A&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Aimei Cao</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/action/doSearch?text1=Yan%2C+Z&amp;field1=Contrib\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Zhu Yan</span></a>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"authorName\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, 