g</span></a><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-45Ligh, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(32,32,32); LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/doi/abs/10.1210/jc.2013-3276#fn1\" target=\"_blank\"><sup><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">*</span></sup></a></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"publicationContentDoi\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">DOI:</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-75Bold, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(0,101,121)\" href=\"http://dx.doi.org/10.1210/jc.2013-3276\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">http://dx.doi.org/10.1210/jc.2013-3276</span></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"publicationContentReceivedDate\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Received: August 24, 2013</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"publicationContentAcceptedDate\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Accepted: November 06, 2013</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"publicationContentEpubDate\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Published Online: January 16, 2014</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"></div></div>\r\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-55Roma, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">\r\n<div class=\"tabs tabs-widget\" style=\"OVERFLOW: hidden; MARGIN: 0px 0px 20px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<ul class=\"tab-nav\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 13px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.55em; TEXT-ALIGN: right; PADDING-TOP: 0.55em; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0.5em 0px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">\r\n<li class=\"active\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif; MARGIN: 0px; DISPLAY: inline\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-TOP: rgb(222,222,222) 1px solid; HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-57Cn, 'Arial Narrow', helvetica, arial, sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(222,222,222) 1px solid; BORDER-BOTTOM-STYLE: solid; TEXT-TRANSFORM: uppercase; COLOR: rgb(100,100,114); PADDING-BOTTOM: 5px; BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); PADDING-TOP: 6px; PADDING-LEFT: 12px; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(222,222,222) 1px solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 12px\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/doi/abs/10.1210/jc.2013-3276\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">ABSTRACT</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></a> </li>\r\n<li style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif; MARGIN: 0px; DISPLAY: inline\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word\" href=\"http://press.endocrine.org/doi/pdf/10.1210/jc.2013-3276\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">PDF</span></a></li></ul>\r\n<div class=\"tab-content\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><article class=\"article\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 13px; COLOR: rgb(33,33,33); LINE-HEIGHT: 17px\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-75Bold, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(0,101,121)\" name=\"abstract\" target=\"_blank\"></a>\r\n<div class=\"sectionInfo\" style=\"OVERFLOW: hidden; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<div class=\"sectionHeading\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-57Cn, 'Arial Narrow', helvetica, arial, sans-serif; POSITION: relative; FLOAT: left; COLOR: rgb(68,102,125); PADDING-BOTTOM: 5px; PADDING-TOP: 20px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: auto auto 7px 0px; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WIDTH: 406px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Abstract</span></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"abstractSection\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<div class=\"NLM_sec NLM_sec_level_1\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-75Bold, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(0,101,121)\" name=\"_i1\" target=\"_blank\"></a>\r\n<div class=\"sectionInfo\" style=\"OVERFLOW: hidden; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<div class=\"sectionHeading\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-57Cn, 'Arial Narrow', helvetica, arial, sans-serif; POSITION: relative; FLOAT: left; COLOR: rgb(89,95,57); PADDING-BOTTOM: 5px; PADDING-TOP: 20px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: auto auto 7px 0px; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 22px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WIDTH: 406px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Context:</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"sectionJumpTo\" style=\"POSITION: relative; FLOAT: right; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; WIDTH: 174px\"></div></div>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Living in a prediabetes state significantly increases a patient's risk for both diabetes and cardiovascular disease. Tianqi capsule, containing 10 Chinese herbal medicines, is used in China for the treatment of type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM).</span></p></div>\r\n<div class=\"NLM_sec NLM_sec_level_1\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-75Bold, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(0,101,121)\" name=\"_i2\" target=\"_blank\"></a>\r\n<div class=\"sectionInfo\" style=\"OVERFLOW: hidden; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<div class=\"sectionHeading\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-57Cn, 'Arial Narrow', helvetica, arial, sans-serif; POSITION: relative; FLOAT: left; COLOR: rgb(89,95,57); PADDING-BOTTOM: 5px; PADDING-TOP: 20px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: auto auto 7px 0px; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 22px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WIDTH: 406px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Objective:</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"sectionJumpTo\" style=\"POSITION: relative; FLOAT: right; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; WIDTH: 174px\"></div></div>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">The purpose of this study was to assess whether Tianqi prevented T2DM in subjects with impaired glucose tolerance (IGT) over the course of a 12-month treatment.</span></p></div>\r\n<div class=\"NLM_sec NLM_sec_level_1\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-75Bold, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(0,101,121)\" name=\"_i3\" target=\"_blank\"></a>\r\n<div class=\"sectionInfo\" style=\"OVERFLOW: hidden; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<div class=\"sectionHeading\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-57Cn, 'Arial Narrow', helvetica, arial, sans-serif; POSITION: relative; FLOAT: left; COLOR: rgb(89,95,57); PADDING-BOTTOM: 5px; PADDING-TOP: 20px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: auto auto 7px 0px; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 22px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WIDTH: 406px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Methods:</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"sectionJumpTo\" style=\"POSITION: relative; FLOAT: right; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; WIDTH: 174px\"></div></div>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Individuals with IGT were randomly allocated in a double-blind manner to receive Tianqi (n = 210) or a placebo (n = 210) for 12 months. Oral glucose tolerance tests were conducted every 3 months to assess the development of diabetes or restoration to normal glucose tolerance. All subjects received the same lifestyle education. The primary endpoint was the conversion of IGT to T2DM. Body weight and body mass index were observed. Adverse effects were monitored.</span></p></div>\r\n<div class=\"NLM_sec NLM_sec_level_1\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-75Bold, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(0,101,121)\" name=\"_i4\" target=\"_blank\"></a>\r\n<div class=\"sectionInfo\" style=\"OVERFLOW: hidden; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<div class=\"sectionHeading\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-57Cn, 'Arial Narrow', helvetica, arial, sans-serif; POSITION: relative; FLOAT: left; COLOR: rgb(89,95,57); PADDING-BOTTOM: 5px; PADDING-TOP: 20px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: auto auto 7px 0px; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 22px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WIDTH: 406px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Results:</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"sectionJumpTo\" style=\"POSITION: relative; FLOAT: right; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; WIDTH: 174px\"></div></div>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Of the 420 enrolled subjects with IGT, 389 completed the trial (198 in the Tianqi group and 191 in the placebo group). At the end of the 12-month trial, 36 subjects in the Tianqi group (18.18%) and 56 in the placebo group (29.32%) had developed diabetes (</span><i><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">P</span></i><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">= .01). There was a significant difference in the number of subjects who had normal glucose tolerance at the end of the study between the Tianqi and placebo groups (n = 125, 63.13%, and n = 89, 46.60%, respectively;</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><i><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">P</span></i><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">= .001). Cox's proportional hazards model analysis showed that Tianqi reduced the risk of diabetes by 32.1% compared with the placebo. No severe adverse events occurred in the trial. There were no statistical differences in body weight and body mass index changes between the Tianqi group and the placebo group during the 12-month trial.</span></p></div>\r\n<div class=\"NLM_sec NLM_sec_level_1\" style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\"><a class=\"con_link\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-75Bold, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(0,101,121)\" name=\"_i5\" target=\"_blank\"></a>\r\n<div class=\"sectionInfo\" style=\"OVERFLOW: hidden; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5\">\r\n<div class=\"sectionHeading\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: HelveticaNeueW01-57Cn, 'Arial Narrow', helvetica, arial, sans-serif; POSITION: relative; FLOAT: left; COLOR: rgb(89,95,57); PADDING-BOTTOM: 5px; PADDING-TOP: 20px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: auto auto 7px 0px; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 22px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WIDTH: 406px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Conclusions:</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"sectionJumpTo\" style=\"POSITION: relative; FLOAT: right; DISPLAY: inline-block; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; WIDTH: 174px\"></div></div>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-LEFT: 18px; LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, sans-serif\">Treatment with a Tianqi capsule for 12 months significantly decreased the incidence of T2DM in subjects with IGT, and this herbal drug was safe to use</span></p></div></div></article></div></div></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>위 논문은&nbsp;&nbsp;JCEM이라는&nbsp;저널에 실린 연구 논문입니다. </p>\r\n<p>JCEM 저널은&nbsp;인용지수 6.43인 국제적으로 인정받는 저널이죠.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
